summary: An ordinance relating to the eminent domain proceedings for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of land and other property in Block 6, Replat of 12th Avenue Addition to the City of Seattle, for park and playground purposes, pursuant to Ordinance No. 67752; providing for the rejection of the awards therein, for the discontinuance of such proceedings and for the repeal of Ordinance No. 67752; and declaring an emergency.
